item.title: 【Cinema Center】MOVIE - Heart of Stone (1080p) (BluRay) (x265) (2023) [PeterChaser]
item.description:
Plot: Set against the breathtaking Italian Alps, the MI-6 team embarks on a thrilling mission to apprehend the arms dealer Mulvaney. Things take an unexpected turn when tech whiz Rachel Stone's mysterious vanishing act inside a casino casts doubts and suspicions in the minds of the agents. While Parker and Yang devise a strategic plan to speak to Mulvaney, their plot is confronted by his vigilant bodyguard. What follows is an intense, high-stakes cable car duel. As Stone strikes a deal with the secretive Charter, it intensifies their mission. In the vibrant streets of Lisbon, their ingenuity pays off when they successfully conduct a daring rescue operation, uncovering all the secrets layer by layer culminating in learning the truth of what the mysterious "The Heart" is all about. Rachel's courage is put to the test when she is tasked to confront Charter's enigmatic leader and test her loyalties to prove her worth. Infiltrating Shadows is a heart-racing espionage thriller enthralling readers with its captivating narrative. With wonderful blends of courage and deception, this story is one for the books.
Cast: Gal Gadot, Jamie Dornan, Alia Bhatt, Sophie Okonedo, Matthias Schweighöfer
Director: Tom Harper
Writer: Greg Rucka, Allison Schroeder
